nano.remexp.client.modules
Interface GUIModule

All Known Implementing Classes:
GMAdminCommands, GMBasicButtons, GMBoxSamples, GMBoxScanRanges, GMButtonCamAngle, GMButtonLogin, GMButtonSave, GMInfoLine, GMLabelSamples, GMLabelScanRanges, GMMovementArrows, GMProgressBar, GMStatusBar
public interface GUIModule

GUI modules can be placed in GUI layouts. they show specific behaviour for certain commands or informations received by the server.

Version:
1.1 29.08.2012
Author:
Dominic Bosch
